data.title: gauri pradhan: Hiten Tejwani and Gauri Pradhan: Shooting in Kashmir was not that difficult
data.meta_description: Actor-couple Hiten Tejwani and Gauri Pradhan are all excited to make their comeback together after eight years. The couple will be seen playing the lead in the new show 'Pashmina'. In an exclusive interview with ETimes TV, the duo said that they are happy to get back on-screen together. They also shared that shooting Kashmir is one interesting factor about the show and the same shall hopefully interest the viewers too.#nishantsinghmalkhani #hitentejwani #Gauri Pradhan #ishasharma #pashmina
